    Contains GUI classes that allow embedding the browser in a Java Swing application.

    Platform initialization classes.
    org.lobobrowser.primary.action
    Contains Browser Action
    org.lobobrowser.primary.ext
    Contains primary extension
    org.lobobrowser.ua
    Contains interfaces that need to be implemented by a browser (like Lobo) in order to service Lobo extensions.
